# Board Observer - Project Overview

AI-powered meeting intelligence platform for enterprise board governance.

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: Next.js 14, React 18, Tailwind CSS, ShadCN UI
- **Backend**: Node.js, Express, Prisma, PostgreSQL
- **Real-time**: Socket.io, WebSockets
- **AI Services**: Recall.ai, OpenAI, ElevenLabs (mocked by default)

## Port Configuration (Non-Standard)
| Service    | Port | Purpose |
|------------|------|---------|
| Frontend   | 4280 | Next.js dev server |
| Backend    | 4281 | Express API |
| PostgreSQL | 5481 | Database |
| Redis      | 6381 | Rate limiting |

## Quick Commands
```bash
make agent-setup   # Complete setup
make agent-start   # Start servers
make agent-test    # Run tests
make agent-verify  # Verify health
make agent-stop    # Stop all
```

